rounded in the direction @var{rnd}.
Just changes the sign if @var{rop} and @var{op} are the same variable.
@end deftypefun

@deftypefun int mpfr_mul_2ui (mpfr_t @var{rop}, mpfr_t @var{op1}, unsigned long int @var{op2}, mp_rnd_t @var{rnd})
